author: Kurzgesagt – In a Nutshell
description:
The world is filling with low effort AI content… but we’d rather quit than make AI slop. That’s why the 12,026 Human Era Calendar matters so much to us: it’s a celebration of real human curiosity, made by the talented artists and researchers behind kurzgesagt. 
Each copy supports our videos, art, and ideas we love to share, while also filling your home with twelve stunning prints and fascinating stories.
✨ Get yours now: https://shop.kgs.link/12-026
